進階搜尋






























       　






查詢範圍：「 不限欄位=陳慧玲   」


顯示範圍：第1、2、3、4、5、6、7、8、9�筆 論文書目資料
顯示格式：全部欄位
      共&nbsp9&nbsp筆




------------------------------------------------------------------------ 
      第 1 筆 ---------------------------------------------------------------------




系統識別號
U0084-0406201221590300


論文名稱(中文) 
      
影響高雄市國小學校效能因素之研究


論文名稱(英文) 
      
A Study on the Elements Affecting the School Effectiveness
of Elementary Schools in Kaohsiung City


校院名稱
樹德科技大學


系所名稱(中)
經營管理研究所


系所名稱(英)
Graduate School of Business and Administration


學年度
100


學期
2


出版年
101


研究生(中文)
黃淑貞


學號
s99733117


學位類別
碩士


語文別
中文


口試日期
2012-05-29


論文頁數
198頁


口試委員
指導教授-廖冠傑
委員-朱國光
委員-林顯輝



關鍵字(中)
學校效能教師教學品質學生學習表現學校公共關係學校行政績


關鍵字(英)
School EffectivenessTeaching QualityStudents’ Learning PerformanceSchool Public RelationsSchool Administrative Performance


學科別分類



中文摘要
    本研究旨在瞭解高雄市國小教師對教師教學品質、學生學習表現、學校公共關係、學校行政績效與學校效能的現況，並分別針對不同的背景變項，在教師教學品質、學生學習表現、學校公共關係、學校行政績效與學校效能上的差異情形加以探討；其次，分析五者之間的關係；最後本研究試圖對這些因素的影響進行驗證。    本研究採文獻分析與問捲調查研究，針對高雄市241所國小371位教師為施測對象，獲得有效問捲358份。蒐集的資料以t考驗、單因子變異數分析、Scheffe 事後考驗法、pearson 相關、多元迴歸分析等統計方法進行分析與處理。    本研究發現，教師教學品質愈高，學生學習表現愈好；學校公共關係愈佳與學校行政績效愈高時，學校的效能也呈現愈好的情況；進一步探討各項因素的子構面對學校效能的影響後，發現：（1）行政運作的績效的高低對於教學品質效能與學校行政效能是否發揮之影響力最大；（2）學生學習態度的優劣對於學生學習表現與親師關係效能是否能發揮之影響力最大；（3）提升行政運作績效，對於整體學校效能的發揮能產生最佳的成效。


英文摘要
     The purpose of this study attempts to investigate the current situations of the Teaching Quality, Students’ Learning Performance, School Public Relations, School Administrative Performance, and School Effectiveness in Kaohsiung City . And it will focus on different variables to discuss the differences between Teaching Quality, Students’ Learning Performance, School Public Relations, School Administrative Performance and School Effectiveness. Then we analyze the relationship of the above mentioned. At last, the study tries to prove the affect of these factors.     The research use literature analysis and questionnaire. The samples were picked up 371 teachers from 241 public elementary schools in Kaohsiung City, and gained 358 valid samples. The data analyzed by various statistical methods and included : t-test, one-way ANOVA, Scheffe method, Pearson correlation and the multiple regression analysis.     The results of the study show the more positive Teaching Quality, the better Students’ Learning Performance and the more positive School Public Relations and School Administrative Performance, the better School Effectiveness. After further discussion about the factors which may affect the School Effectiveness, we find as below: (1)The most important factor about Teaching Quality and School Administrative Performance result from Administrative Performance. (2)The excellent learning attitude of students will affect Students’ Performance and the relationship between teachers and students. (3)When we promote School Administrative Performance ,it would improve the whole School Effectiveness to achieve the best effect.


