      第 4 筆 ---------------------------------------------------------------------




系統識別號
U0084-1206201515411300


論文名稱(中文) 
      
探討戒護管理人員工作壓力對休閒活動涉入之影響


論文名稱(英文) 
      
Explore the effect of working stress on Leisure activities involved by controllers in the prison


校院名稱
樹德科技大學


系所名稱(中)
經營管理研究所


系所名稱(英)
Graduate School of Business and Administration


學年度
103


學期
2


出版年
104


研究生(中文)
陳坤豊


學號
s13733215


學位類別
碩士


語文別
中文


口試日期
2015-05-16


論文頁數
90頁


口試委員
指導教授-蘇明俊
委員-張景弘
委員-許龍池



關鍵字(中)
戒護管理人員工作壓力休閒涉入


關鍵字(英)
controllerjob pressuresleisure involvement


學科別分類



中文摘要
監獄戒護管理人員因工作有高度危險性且需輪班，造成工作壓力。當個人感受到工作壓力時，會產生心理、生理上的相關症狀，透過休閒活動的參與降低工作壓力及舒緩身心，基於休閒參與的涉入程度會影響工作壓力的有效紓解，本研究探討戒護管理人員工作壓力對休閒活動涉入的影響，研究對象為臺灣地區的戒護人員，以立意取樣的方法，以臺南監獄及臺南看守所編制內之戒護管理人員427人為樣本，工具為「工作壓力與休閒涉入量表」，有效問捲390份。所得資料以描述性統計瞭解分佈情形；以t檢定及變異數分析的方法瞭解不同資料的差異性；以迴歸分析瞭解相互影響的情形。發現：1.不同背景變項對工作壓力有顯著影響。2.不同背景變項對休閒活動涉入除年齡、年資、勤務班別、職稱有顯著影響外，其他並無顯著影響。3.不同的工作壓力對休閒活動涉入有顯著影響。4.工作壓力對休閒活動涉入影響之預測力結果顯示，在工作壓力的構面中「工作外部」及「角色對立」能夠有效預測休閒活動涉入中的「人際互動」，且具有顯著影響。建議監所主管機關多鼓勵管理人員多從事休閒活動，促進身體活動力及心肺能力，以有效紓緩工作壓力，促進管理人員的身心健康。


英文摘要
The guard and control section controllers of prison have a shift because their work is more dangerous than other works, and it makes them under pressure. When one person is under pressure, they will have psychological and physiologic symptom. Through taking part in the leisure activities could help them reduce the pressure and relax themselves. The degree of taking part in leisure activities will affect that how they relax themselves. This research probes that the influence of guard and control section controllers how to take part in leisure activities in order to reduce their working pressure. The objects are the controllers of Tainan Prison and Tainan Detention Center. The research uses the questionnaire survey method and the scales, and gets 390 effective questionnaires. We use descriptive statistics to analyze the information and the result, and use t-test and analysis of variance to understand the difference among information. Then, we also use regression analysis to understand the degree of influence. We discover the following results. (1) The different background variables affect the degree of working pressure. (2) Age, seniority, shift work and the job title will affect the different background variables of leisure activities, and there is no influence on other variables. (3) Different degree of working pressure affects the choice of leisure activities. (4) The anticipatable result reveals that 「the external work」 and 「the opposition of roles」 in the part of working pressure could effectively forecast 「interpersonal interaction」 and it has apparent influence. Therefore, we suggest that the authorities should encourage controllers to take part in the leisure activities because it can promote the body activity and the function of heart and lung. It also can reduce working pressure effectively and makes controllers healthy.


論文目次
