關鍵字(中)
3D模型設計虛擬人物造型設計角色創作


關鍵字(英)
3D Model DesignVisual CharacterStyling DesignCharacter Design


學科別分類



中文摘要
資訊科技快速成長使行動裝置普及率迅速提升，帶動數位遊戲市場蓬勃發展。如何滿足玩家對遊戲的偏好，提升玩家對電腦遊戲的涉入程度有其重要性。如何維繫與電腦遊戲玩家之間的長期緊密關係，提高顧客忠誠度，以尋求永續經營，乃遊戲開發商應深究之議題。因此，本研究結合數位遊戲與流行時尚兩大設計領域，以期使電腦遊戲內容更趨向多元化。透過創作之擬真人物模擬服裝穿搭及舞臺展演遊戲作品，提供電腦遊戲玩家於視覺上與真實生活更為貼近之感受。為更進一步瞭解電腦遊戲玩家對創作作品之接受程度，以高雄地區遊戲玩家為研究對象，共回收有效問捲72份。研究結果發現：1.電腦遊戲玩家對此擬真遊戲持正面使用態度評價。2.電腦遊戲玩家對此擬真遊戲願意再次使用及向他人推薦之行為意向。3.設計領域玩家與非設計領域玩家對此擬真遊戲之感受度相近。4.設計領域玩家與非設計領域玩家願意再次使用、公開推薦或向他人介紹此創作作品。


英文摘要
Owing to the increasing demand from the fast-growing popularity of mobile devices, Information Technology (IT) has been developing rapidly, which leads to the increasing market of the digital game industry. Thus, how to meet the game players’ requirement and expectation become vital to the success of the digital game business. As regards, the way to maintain the long-term relationship between the digital game and related customer departs on the custom loyalty management, which has one of the crucial research in digital game design and development. Since the fashion industry requires creativeness of clothing design, styling and associated stage and exhibition design, the 3D simulation technique might be helpful to the customer relation management. Therefore, the aim of this research is to design and propose an overall design strategy of virtual character design based on the fashion trend of cloth and styling in Kaohsiung city. The questionnaire method was employed to validate the relation between the customer relation elements and 3D simulation design elements. Totally, 72 questionnaires were collected, As a result: 1.There is a positive relation between "The Use of 3D Simulation" and “Attitude to Play the Game”.2.There is a positive relation between “The Use of 3D Simulation" and “Intention to Recommend the Game to New Customer”.3.There is no significant effect of “Designer Background” on “3D Simulation Acceptance”.4.There is a significant effect of “Designer Background” on “Willing to Play the Game Continually” and “Willing to Recommend the Game to Others in Public”.


論文目次
